init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Son, I'm not really number one here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But, you know, if I had to do it all over again?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not sure how this will affect our relationship, but I hope it can be better."
